No. 10-1512. James DeWeese, Judge, Court of Common Pleas, Richland County, Ohio, Petitioner v. American Civil Liberties Union of Ohio Foundation, Inc. 565 U.S. 930, 132 S. Ct. 368,

181 L. Ed. 2d 234,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 7025. October 3, 2011.

Motion of Foundation for Moral Law for leave to file a brief as amicus curiae out of time granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Sixth Circuit denied.

Same case below, 633 F.3d 424.
